main.record

Interface IRecord

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActionRecord, PerformanceRecord, SaleRecord, VestRecord 

    public interface IRecord
    The IRecord interface is used for testing and in the building of our main.record classes, this is a representation of all our action records.
    Since:
    2016-07-11
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
